 buvez", "words": [87, 88, 89, 90, 91, 92]}, {"id": 15, "text": "BOIRE", "words": [93]}, {"id": 16, "text": "PRENDRE Ils prenn-ent Nous pren-ons", "words": [94, 95, 96, 97, 98]}, {"id": 17, "text": "Vous prenez", "words": [99, 100]}, {"id": 18, "text": "—", "words": [101]}, {"id": 19, "text": "= — — —", "words": [102, 103, 104, 105]}, {"id": 20, "text": "—", "words": [106]}, {"id": 21, "text": "Il faut que", "words": [107, 108, 109]}, {"id": 22, "text": "(Et : venir, recevoir, acheter, jeter, etc.)", "words": [110, 111, 112, 113, 114, 115, 116]}, {"id": 23, "text": "M Verbes irréguliers ÊTRE", "words": [117, 118, 119, 120]}, {"id": 24, "text": "sois", "words": [121]}, {"id": 25, "text": "sois", "words": [122]}, {"id": 26, "text": "soit soyons", "words": [123, 124]}, {"id": 27, "text": "soyez soient", "words": [125, 126]}, {"id": 28, "text": "que je que tu qu'il", "words": [127, 128, 129, 130, 131]}, {"id": 29, "text": "que nous que vous qu'ils", "words": [132, 133, 134, 135, 136]}, {"id": 30, "text": "que j' que tu qu'il", "words": [137, 138, 139, 140, 141]}, {"id": 31, "text": "que nous que vous qu'ils", "words": [142, 143, 144, 145, 146]}, {"id": 32, "text": "POUVOIR que je puisse", "words": [147, 148, 149, 150]}, {"id": 33, "text": "240 e deux cent quarante", "words": [151, 152, 153, 154, 155]}, {"id": 34, "text": "que vous puissiez", "words": [156, 157, 158]}, {"id": 35, "text": "que que tu qu'il", "words": [159, 160, 161, 162]}, {"id": 36, "text": "que nous que vous qu'ils", "words": [163, 164, 165, 166, 167]}, {"id": 37, "text": "je nous vous", "words": [168, 169, 170]}, {"id": 38, "text": "que que", "words": [171, 172]}, {"id": 39, "text": "que que que", "words": [173, 174, 175]}, {"id": 40, "text": "je", "words": [176]}, {"id": 41, "text": "ALLER", "words": [177]}, {"id": 42, "text": "aille ailles aille allions alliez aillent", "words": [178, 179, 180, 181, 182, 183]}, {"id": 43, "text": "que je que tu qu'il", "words": [184, 185, 186, 187, 188]}, {"id": 44, 